```plantuml
@startuml usds_justice40-tool

actor User
participant "React App" as ReactApp
participant "API Server" as APIServer
participant "ETL Runner" as ETLRunner
participant "Scoring Module" as ScoringModule
participant "Map Generator" as MapGenerator
participant "Data Source" as DataSource

== User Interaction ==
User -> ReactApp: Load Map
ReactApp -> APIServer: Request Map Data

== Data Pipeline Execution ==
APIServer -> ETLRunner: Trigger ETL Process
ETLRunner -> DataSource: Extract Data
DataSource --> ETLRunner: Return Raw Data
ETLRunner -> ETLRunner: Transform Data
ETLRunner -> ETLRunner: Load Data to Data Lake

== Scoring Process ==
APIServer -> ScoringModule: Calculate Scores
ScoringModule -> DataSource: Retrieve Data
ScoringModule -> ScoringModule: Apply Scoring Methodologies
ScoringModule --> APIServer: Return Scores

== Map Tile Generation ==
APIServer -> MapGenerator: Generate Map Tiles
MapGenerator -> DataSource: Retrieve GeoJSON Data
MapGenerator -> MapGenerator: Process GeoJSON
MapGenerator -> MapGenerator: Create Tiles
MapGenerator --> APIServer: Return Map Tiles

== Response to User ==
APIServer --> ReactApp: Send Map Data and Scores
ReactApp --> User: Display Map and Scores

@enduml
```